Class Guano

A class to represent a Guano metadata chunk included in a .wav file. The guano data should be extracted with Tools.Get_WAV_MetaData(wavfilename) and the string can be parsed with ParseGuanoChunk(string chunk) which will return an instance of this class. The class copes with a number of known fields for GUANO data according to specification 1.0 but is intended to work with GUANO data embedded by the Android App BatRecorder.
